# WeRide Secures Exclusive AV Partnership in Ras Al Khaimah Ahead of 2027 Casino Resort

**Source**: User Fact Check / RAKTA
**Published**: 2025-10-02 00:00:00
**Link**: https://www.rakta.gov.ae/en/news/weride-exclusive-partnership-2025

WeRide (WRD) has been named the exclusive partner for Ras Al Khaimah's smart transportation strategy. The company officially launched Robotaxi GXR and Robobus pilot operations with RAKTA on October 2, 2025. WeRide is the first and only AV company with active operations in the emirate. This deal aligns with the Wynn Al Marjan Island resort development - the Middle East's first luxury casino resort scheduled to open early 2027. The AVs are expected to serve the transport ecosystem for this major tourism development.

title: Fed Rate Outlook 2026: Rates to Remain at 3.5-3.75% with Potential Cuts
source: iShares/J.P. Morgan/Goldman Sachs
published_date: 2026-01-18 18:32:51
url: https://www.ishares.com/us/insights/fed-outlook-2026-interest-rate-forecast
---

We believe the most likely path for Fed policy in 2026 is for the central bank to bring rates down from the current range of 3.50% to 3.75% to closer to 3% over the course of the year.

Ultimately, Fed policy in 2026 will depend on economic data, particularly on inflation and the labor market. But Fed Chairman Jay Powell’s term expires in May 2026 and a potential new chair may result in some uncertainty.

Given the expected path of Fed policy, we see opportunities for investors in the belly of the yield curve, managing interest rate risk with bond laddering and seeking higher income outside of core bonds.
